d-news%2Fnepal-teen-becomes-youngest-to-climb-worlds-8-000m-peaks-6750198%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnnecessary%26quot%3B%3A%20Omar%20Abdullah%20On%20Centre%20Nominating%205%20MLAs%20To%20J%26amp%3BK%20Assembly%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENational%20Conference%20(NC)%20leader%20Omar%20Abdullah%20has%20expressed%20strong%20reservations%20about%20the%20Centre's%20potential%20move%20of%20nominating%20five%20BJP%20MLAs%20to%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20cautioned%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%20Manoj%20Sinha%20against%20making%20these%20nominations%2C%20warning%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20unnecessary%20political%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20rules%20governing%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20nominate%20five%20members%20to%20the%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20which%20currently%20consists%20of%2090%20elected%20members.%20If%20these%20five%20nominees%20are%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20is%20speculated%2C%20it%20would%20increase%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20assembly%20to%2095%20members%2C%20thereby%20shifting%20the%20majority%20mark%20from%2046%20to%2048.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20suggest%20them%20to%20not%20do%20it%20(nominate%20from%20BJP).%20Nominating%20these%20five%20will%20not%20change%20the%20government%2C%20so%20what%20is%20the%20use%20of%20it%3F%20You%20would%20unnecessarily%20nominate%20five%20people%20to%20sit%20in%20Opposition%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanalysing-unexpected-results-rahul-gandhi-on-congress-haryana-loss-6749828%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAnalysing%20Unexpected%20Results%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20On%20Congress's%20Mixed%20Bag%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20would%20still%20be%20unable%20to%20form%20the%20government%20-%20having%20won%2029%20seats%20-%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20majority%20mark%20would%20narrow%20the%20NC-Congress%20alliance's%20lead%20to%20just%20one%20seat%20above%20the%20required%20threshold.%20%26quot%3BIndependent%20candidates%20are%20talking%20to%20us%2C%20and%20they%20will%20join%20us%2C%20so%20our%20lead%20will%20go%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Abdullah%20also%20warned%20of%20a%20potential%20legal%20battle%20if%20the%20nominations%20proceeded.%20%26quot%3BThere%20would%20be%20a%20fight%20as%20we%20would%20have%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20appeal%20against%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20could%20strain%20J%26amp%3BK's%20relationship%20with%20the%20Centre%20at%20a%20time%20when%20cooperation%20is%20crucial.%20%26quot%3BThere%20would%20be%20tensions%20in%20our%20relations%20with%20the%20Centre%20from%20the%20first%20day%2C%20a%20relation%20that%20we%20want%20to%20build.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NC-Congress%20alliance%20emerged%20victorious%20in%20the%20first%20J%26amp%3BK%20elections%20since%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20securing%2049%20out%20of%2090%20seats.%20Mr%20Abdullah%20won%20both%20the%20constituencies%20he%20contested%20from%20-%20%C2%A0Budgam%20and%20Ganderbal%20-%20with%20a%20comfortable%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fj-k-assembly-election-result-omar-abdullah-ndtv-interview-pm-an-honourable-man-hope-he-omar-abdullahs-key-ask-after-j-k-win-6745271%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BPM%20An%20Honourable%20Man%2C%20Hope%20He...%26quot%3B%3A%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20Key%20Ask%20After%20J%26amp%3BK%20Win%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%2042%20seats%20for%20the%20NC%20and%20six%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20alliance%20has%20comfortably%20crossed%20the%20initial%20majority%20mark%20of%2046.%20In%20contra