h%20Centre%20(BARC)%20with%20support%20from%20the%20Electronics%20Corporation%20of%20India%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20and%20other%20Indian%20industry%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MACE%20observatory%20is%20touted%20to%20place%20India%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20cosmic%20ray%20research%20globally%20by%20allowing%20scientists%20to%20study%20high-energy%20gamma%20rays.%20This%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20the%20universe's%20most%20energetic%20events%2C%20such%20as%20supernovae%2C%20black%20holes%2C%20and%20gamma-ray%20bursts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20its%20formal%20inauguration%2C%20the%20telescope%20produced%20high-quality%20work%20detecting%20gamma%20ray%20flares%20as%20far%20away%20as%20200%20million%20light%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20MACE%20observatory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMACE%20is%2021%20metres%20in%20diameter%2C%20175%20tonnes%20heavy%2C%20has%20reflector%20area%20of%20356%20sqm%20and%201%2C424%20diamond-turned%20metallic%20mirror%20facets%2C%20712%20actuators%2C%201%2C088%20photo-multiplier%20tubes%2C%20and%2068%20camera%20modules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20lightweight%20construction%20and%20features%20high%20strength%20and%20temperature%20endurance.%20Reflector%20surface%20measuring%20over%20350%20square%20metres%20(sqm)%20comprises%20highly%20reflective%20diamond-turned%20custom-built%20metallic%20mirror%20facets%20that%20are%20required%20to%20be%20aligned%20with%20an%20accuracy%20of%202%20mm%20over%20parabolic%20surface.%20The%20camera%20at%20the%20focal%20point%20contains%20a%20number%20of%20photomultiplier%20tubes%20mounted%20with%20specialised%20assembly%20to%20enhance%20light%20collection%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltrafast%20backend%20electronics%20with%20nanosecond%20digitization%20electronics%20is%20optimised%20for%20low-power%20and%20-temperature%20operations.%20Extreme%20weather%20conditions%20restrict%20transport%20to%20six-eight%20months%20a%20year%20and%20affect%20the%20availability%20of%20trained%20personnel%20on%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20telescope%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGamma%20rays%20do%20not%20reach%20the%20Earth's%20surface%20as%20they%20are%20stopped%20by%20the%20atmosphere.%20However%2C%20interaction%20with%20the%20atmosphere%20creates%20high-energy%20particles%20that%20travel%20faster%20than%20the%20speed%20of%20flight%20and%20emit%20Cherenkov%20radiation%20which%20is%20akin%20to%20a%20sonic%20boom.%20The%20mirrors%20and%20cameras%20capture%20these%20flashes%20and%20trace%20them%20back%20to%20its%20cosmic%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Hanle%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20has%20been%20carefully%20chosen%20for%20its%20unique%20scientific%20advantages%20as%20Hanle%20offers%20extremely%20low%20light%20pollution%20required%20for%20gamma%20ray%20observations.%20The%20longitudinal%20advantage%20of%20its%20location%20enables%20MACE%20to%20observe%20sources%20invisible%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHanle%20is%20like%20heaven%20for%20gamma%20ray%20astronomers%20with%20its%20dark%20skies%2C%20low%20humidity%20and%20almost%20no%20air%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dr%20AK%20Mohanty%2C%20chairman%2C%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%20and%20India's%20nuclear%20chief.%20He%20said%20another%20few%20more%20gamma%20ray%20telescopes%20could%20be%20built%20here%2C%20making%20Hanle%20the%20go-to%20place%20for%20global%20astronomers%2C%20some%20with%20international%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728453600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fi2121028_mace-telescope-ladakh_625x300_09_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworlds-highest-gamma-ray-telescope-inaugurated-in-ladakh-6749396%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Major%20Atmospheric%20Cherenkov%20Experiment%20observatory%2C%20the%20largest%20imagi