ree%20external%20members%2C%20voted%205%3A1%20to%20keep%20the%20repo%20rate%20unchanged.%20It%20had%20last%20changed%20rates%20in%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MPC%20also%20kept%20the%20growth%20projection%20unchanged%20at%207.2%20per%20cent%20for%20the%20current%20financial%20year.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728450240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F9i0la298_rbi-governor_625x300_08_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbi-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-for-the-10th-consecutive-time-6749173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20has%20kept%20its%20key%20interest%20rate%20unchanged%20for%20the%20tenth%20consecutive%20time%2C%20its%20governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20announced%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbi-keeps-key-lending-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-for-the-10th-consecutive-time-6749173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20policy%3A%20MPC%20keeps%20repo%20rate%20unchanged%20at%206.5%25%2C%20shifts%20stance%20to%20neutral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728450146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-06%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1717747437-6982.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Frbi-mpc-keeps-repo-rate-unchanged-at-6-5-changes-stance-to-neutral-124100900247_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20that%20India's%20real%20GDP%20grew%20by%206.7%20per%20cent%20in%20Q1.%20For%20FY25%2C%20the%20RBI%20kept%20its%20GDP%20projection%20unchanged%20at%207.2%20per%20cent%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Frbi-mp