l%20court%20in%20Sealdah.%20It%20charged%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20who%20used%20to%20work%20with%20Kolkata%20Police%20as%20a%20contractual%20staff%2C%20with%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20the%20on-duty%20woman%20doctor.%20The%20statements%20of%20about%20200%20people%20were%20recorded%20in%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faccused-sanjoy-roy-raped-murdered-doctor-cbi-charge-sheet-in-rg-kar-case-6734823%5C%22%3ECBI%20sources%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20detailed%20in%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20largely%20followed%20the%20Kolkata%20Police's%20line%20of%20investigation%20and%20has%20relied%20on%20digital%20and%20material%20evidence%20collected%20by%20them%20along%20with%20to%20establish%20Sanjoy%20Roy's%20presence%20at%20the%20scene%20of%20crime%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20rape-murder.%20CCTV%20footage%20has%20been%20used%20to%20establish%20the%20timings%20of%20his%20movement%20from%203.34%20am%20onwards%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20crime%20(August%209)%2C%20when%20he%20was%20seen%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20trauma%20centre%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%204.03%20am%2C%20the%20accused%20was%20seen%20%E2%80%9Cwearing%20a%20T-shirt%20and%20jeans%2C%20holding%20a%20helmet%20in%20his%20left%20hand%20with%20Bluetooth%20neckband%20earphones%20around%20his%20neck%2C%20moving%20from%20the%20right%20side%20of%20the%20camera%20towards%20the%20ward%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20per%20the%20CBI%20chargesheet.%20At%204.32%20am%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20emerging%20from%20the%20ward%20on%20the%20third%20floor%2C%20helmet%20in%20his%20left%20hand%2C%20but%20without%20the%20neckband%20earphones%20around%20his%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20further%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20Bluetooth%20neckband%20earphone%20was%20seized%20by%20local%20police%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20crime%20on%2009.08.2024.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20used%20as%20a%20crucial%20piece%20of%20evidence%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20to%20nail%20and%20arrest%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20a%20day%20after%20the%20crime.%20The%20Customer%20Acquisition%20Form%20and%20Call%20Detail%20Records%20of%20the%20mobile%20number%20belonging%20to%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20also%20corroborated%20his%20presence%20at%20the%20hospital%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20as%20per%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20earphones%2C%20physical%20evidence%20listed%20by%20the%20CBI%20included%20the%20victim's%20mobile%20phone%20and%20laptop%2C%20accused's%20mobile%2C%20accused's%20blood%20sample%20and%20blood%20and%20viscera%20examined%20during%20the%20autopsy.%20The%20chargesheet%20said%20the%20evidence%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Chandigarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20forensic%20experts%20studied%20jeans%2C%20underwear%2C%20brassiere%2C%20kurti%2C%20blanket%2C%20bedsheets%2C%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%2C%20synthetic%20cotton%2C%20nail%20cuttings%20and%20scrappings%2C%20blood%20sample%2C%20lip%20swab%2C%20endocervical%20swab%2C%20vaginal%20swab%20and%20pubic%20hair%20combing.%20On%20August%2012%2C%20pants%20and%20slippers%20seized%20from%20the%20barracks%20of%20the%20accused%20worn%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crime%20were%20found%20to%20have%20the%20victim's%20blood%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20mentioned.%20Saliva%20belonging%20to%20the%20accused%20has%20been%20detected%20on%20a%20nipple%20swab%20preserved%20during%20the%20autopsy.%20Short%20hair%20belonging%20to%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20were%20lso%20lifted%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%2C%20the%20victim%20died%20due%20to%20asphyxia%2C%20resulting%20from%20a%20combined%20effect%20of%20throttling%20(manual%20strangulation)%20and%20smothering.%20%26quot%3BThe%20injuries%20related%20to%20hymen%2C%20which%20were%20fresh%20in%20origin%2C%20are%20clearly%20indicating%20that%20the%20victim%20had%20suffered%20forceful%20penetrative%20sexual%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%20Injuries%20found%20on%20the%20accused's%20body%20indicated%20the%20use%20of%20blunt%20force%20consistent%20with%20signs%20of%20resistance%20by%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20a%20Kolkata%20court%20took%20cognisance%20of%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI.%20The%20court%20also%20decided%20that%20the%20trial%20of%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20will%20be%20held%20in-camera.%20The%20date%20for%20the%20framing%20of%20charges%2C%20which%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20is%20set%20for%20November%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20Sanjay%20Rai%20spoke%20in%20court%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20told%20the%20court%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20don't%20speak%20all%20the%20blame%20will%20be%20put%20on%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20case%2C%20I%20am%20innocent%2C%26quot%3B%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20rape%20and%20murder%20Accused%20Sanjay%20Rai%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728445260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fomtb15j_sanjoy-roy_625x300_23_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-case-kolkata-rape-murder-cbi-chargesheet-details-how-rg-kar-rape-murder-accused-was-nailed-6748844%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBI%20chargesheet%20filed%20in%20the%20RG%20Kar%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20has%20detailed%20the%20circumstances%2C%20nature%20of%20injuries%2C%20cause%20of%20death%20and%20evidence%20available%20against%20the%20accused.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frg-kar-case-kolkata-rape-murder-cbi-chargesheet-details-how-rg-kar-rape-murder-accused-was-nailed-6748844%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Milton%3A%20How%20to%20stay%20safe%