ith%20storm%20surges%20posing%20severe%20threats%20and%20the%20state%20already%20impacted%20by%20Hurricane%20Helene%2C%20officials%20and%20President%20Biden%20have%20issued%20dire%20warnings%20for%20immediate%20evacuation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhurricane-milton-10-things-to-know-about-category-5-storm-set-to-hit-florida%2Farticleshow%2F114062983.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhurricane-milton-10-things-to-know-about-category-5-storm-set-to-hit-florida%2Famp_articleshow%2F114062983.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhurricane-milton-10-things-to-know-about-category-5-storm-set-to-hit-florida%2Famp_articleshow%2F114062983.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20Seeking%20To%20Cause%20%26quot%3BMayhem%26quot%3B%20In%20UK%20Over%20Support%20For%20Ukraine%3A%20Spy%20Agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussia's%20intelligence%20service%20has%20been%20intent%20on%20causing%20%26quot%3Bmayhem%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20UK%20because%20of%20London's%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Britain's%20domestic%20intelligence%20service%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%20Ken%20McCallum%20also%20said%20MI5%20had%20responded%20to%2020%20Iran-backed%20plots%20since%20January%202022%20that%20presented%20potentially%20lethal%20threats%20to%20British%20citizens%20and%20UK%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20Iran%20had%20turned%20to%20employing%20criminals%20and%20private%20intelligence%20officers%20to%20do%20their%20work%20on%20British%20soil%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Russia%2C%20Britain%20should%20%26quot%3Bexpect%20to%20see%20continued%20acts%20of%20aggression%20here%20at%20home%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20military%20intelligence%20agency%20the%20GRU%20on%20%26quot%3Bsustained%20missions%20to%20generate%20mayhem%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20country's%20streets%2C%20McCallum%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20arson%2C%20sabotage%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Iran%2C%20he%20said%20there%20had%20been%20an%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%20pace%20and%20scale%26quot%3B%20of%20plots%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20events%20unfold%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20MI5%20was%20giving%20its%20%26quot%3Bfullest%20attention%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20risk%20of%20a%20rise%20in%20Iranian-state%20backed%20aggression%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20MI5%20and%20the%20police%20have%20disrupted%2043%20late-stage%20attack%20plots%20since%20March%202017%2C%20saving%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%20lives%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20those%20plotters%20were%20trying%20to%20get%20hold%20of%20firearms%20and%20explosives%2C%20in%20the%20final%20days%20of%20planning%20mass%20murder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20speech%2C%20McCallum%20also%20blamed%20extreme%20right-wing%20ideologies%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bstaggering%26quot%3B%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20children%20being%20investigated%20for%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder-18s%20represent%2013%20percent%20of%20people%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20spy%20agency%20for%20possible%20involvement%20in%20terror%20activities%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20reporters%20at%20MI5's%20Counter%20Terrorism%20Operations%20Centre%20in%20London%20that%20the%20number%20marked%20%26quot%3Ba%20threefold%20increase%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCallum%20said%20the%20internet%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20factor%26quot%3B%20driving%20the%20rise%2C%20describing%20how%20easily%20youngsters%20can%20access%20%26quot%3Binspirational%20and%20instructional%20material%26quot%3B%20from%20their%20bedrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20intelligence%20service%20was%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20many%20cases%20where%20very%20young%20people%20are%20being%20drawn%20into%20poisonous%20online%20extremism%26quot%3B%2C%20singling%20out%20%26quot%3Bcanny%26quot%3B%20internet%20memes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExtreme%20right-wing%20terrorism%20in%20particular%20skews%20heavily%20towards%20young%20people%2C%20driven%20by%20propaganda%20that%20shows%20a%20canny%20understanding%20of%20online%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20really%20a%20consistent%20single%20ideology%20on%20the%20extreme%20right-wing%20side%20and%20that%20is%20what%20has%20skewed%20the%20numbers%20most%20heavily.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20terrorist%20threat%20level%20remains%20at%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%26quot%3B%20--%20the%20third%20highest%20out%20of%20five%20--%20meaning%20an%20attack%20is%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMcCallum%20added%20that%20the%20Islamic%20State%20group%20had%20%26quot%3Bresumed%20efforts%20to%20export%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20in%20the%20last%20year%20inquiries%20into%20plots%20by%20hostile%20states%20had%20surged%20by%2048%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728442860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F2qeertf_london_625x300_09_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-seeking-to-cause-mayhem-in-uk-over-support-for-ukraine-spy-agency-m5-chief-ken-mccallum-6748715%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20and%20Iran%20had%20turned%20to%20employing%20criminals%20and%20private%20intelligence%20officers%20to%20do%20their%20work%20on%20British%20soil%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Britain's%20domestic%20intelligence%20service%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen