%20Lebanon%20into%20Israel.%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20has%20shown%20no%20signs%20of%20letting%20up%2C%20threatened%20to%20continue%20firing%20on%20Israeli%20cities%20and%20towns%20if%20Israeli%20strikes%20on%20Lebanese%20population%20centres%20persisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20been%20simmering%20since%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20a%20devastating%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20killing%20over%20a%20thousand%20civilians.%20Since%20then%2C%20Hezbollah%2C%20a%20key%20ally%20of%20Hamas%2C%20has%20engaged%20in%20sporadic%20exchanges%20of%20fire%20with%20Israeli%20forces.%20Israel%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20vowed%20to%20secure%20its%20northern%20border%20and%20protect%20its%20citizens%20from%20Hezbollah's%20rocket%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah's%20Leadership%20in%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah's%20leadership%20has%20faced%20major%20setbacks%20in%20recent%20weeks.%20In%20late%20September%2C%20Israel%20killed%20its%20leader%20Hassan%20Nasrallah%20in%20an%20airstrike%20on%20Beirut.%20Nasrallah%20had%20led%20Hezbollah%20since%201992%20and%20was%20widely%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20figures%20in%20Lebanon.%20His%20death%20marked%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20group%2C%20but%20Israeli%20strikes%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20In%20October%2C%20Israel%20launched%20another%20bombing%20campaign%20in%20Beirut%2C%20targeting%20Hashem%20Safieddine%2C%20a%20senior%20Hezbollah%20figure%20widely%20believed%20to%20be%20Nasrallah's%20successor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Hezbollah%20has%20not%20confirmed%20Safieddine's%20death%2C%20Netanyahu%20seemed%20to%20suggest%20in%20his%20video%20address%20that%20both%20Nasrallah%20and%20Safieddine%20had%20been%20killed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20in%20his%20address%20said%20Israel%20has%20%26quot%3Bdegraded%20Hezbollah's%20capabilities%3B%20we%20took%20out%20thousands%20of%20terrorists%2C%20including%20%5Blongtime%20Hezbollah%20leader%20Hassan%5D%20Nasrallah%20himself%2C%20and%20Nasrallah's%20replacement%2C%20and%20his%20replacement's%20replacement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20struck%20Hezbollah's%20intelligence%20headquarters%20in%20Beirut...%20this%20is%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20head%20of%20the%20intelligence%20division%2C%20Abu%20Abdullah%20Mortada%2C%26quot%3B%20IDF%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20him%2C%20we%20know%20that%20Hashem%20Safieddine%20was%20there.%20The%20results%20of%20this%20strike%20are%20still%20being%20looked%20into%2C%20Hezbollah%20is%20trying%20to%20hide%20the%20details.%20When%20we%20know%2C%20we%20will%20update%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsrael's%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20already%20targeted%20strongholds%20in%20southern%20and%20eastern%20Lebanon%2C%20Israel's%20latest%20moves%20signal%20a%20shift%20towards%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20with%20civilians%20being%20urged%20to%20evacuate.%20On%20its%20Telegram%20channel%2C%20the%20Israeli%20military%20confirmed%20that%20the%20146th%20Division%20had%20begun%20%26quot%3Blocalised%2C%20targeted%20operational%20activities%26quot%3B%20in%20southwestern%20Lebanon%2C%20directly%20aimed%20at%20Hezbollah%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20have%20not%20spared%20Beirut%2C%20with%20strikes%20targeting%20Hezbollah's%20stronghold%20in%20the%20southern%20suburbs%20of%20the%20city.%20This%20area%20is%20a%20key%20base%20of%20operations%20for%20Hezbollah.%20Israel%20has%20since%20dismantled%20Hezbollah%20tunnels%20leading%20into%20Israeli%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20Remains%20Defiant%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20losses%2C%20Hezbollah%20remains%20defiant.%20Its%20deputy%20leader%20Naim%20Qassem%20declared%20that%20the%20group's%20military%20capabilities%20were%20intact%20and%20that%20they%20were%20prepared%20for%20a%20protracted%20conflict.%20Qassem's%20statement%20came%20even%20as%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20described%20Hezbollah%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbroken%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20whose%20leadership%20had%20been%20decimated%20following%20the%20elimination%20of%20Nasrallah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGallant%20said%20the%20impact%20of%20Israel's%20strikes%2C%20claiming%20that%20Hezbollah's%20command%20structure%20was%20in%20disarray%20and%20that%20the%20group%20lacked%20leadership%20following%20the%20death%20of%20Nasrallah%20and%20other%20key%20figures.%20He%20also%20described%20Hezbollah's%20firepower%20capabilities%20as%20significantly%20diminished%2C%20thanks%20to%20Israel's%20focused%20military%20campaign.%20However%2C%20Hezbollah%20continues%20to%20maintain%20its%20presence%20along%20the%20Lebanese%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Shadow%20of%20Iran%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conflict%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%20The%20group%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20be%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20which%20supplies%20it%20with%20weapons%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20political%20support.%20Israeli%20forces%20have%20clashed%20with%20Iran-backed%20militias%20across%20the%20region%2C%20including%20in%20Syria%20and%20Yemen.%20Just%20this%20week%2C%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%20in%20Damascus%20targeted%20a%20building%20used%20by%20Iran's%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20and%20Hezbollah%2C%20killing%20seven%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20Syrian%20government%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20also%20accused%20Hezbollah%20of%20using%20civilian%20areas%20as%20shields%20for%20their%20military%20operations%2C%20a%20tactic%20that%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation.%20Hezbollah%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20pointed%20to%20the%20heavy%20civilian%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20as%20evidence%20of%20Israel's%20indiscriminate%20use%20of%20force.%20The%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20Gaza%20is%20dire%2C%20with%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%202.4%20million%20residents%20displaced%20at%20leas