ene-just-flooded-tampa-bay-heres-how-much-worse-miltons-surge-could-be%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Tampa%20Bay%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20Milton%20%E2%80%94%20which%20reached%20category%205%20strength%20on%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20%E2%80%94%20could%20bring%20double%20that%2C%20with%20a%20surge%20up%20to%2015%20feet%20and%20wind%20levels%20of%20up%20to%20165%20mph%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhc.noaa.gov%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Hurricane%20Center%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelene's%20surge%20flooded%20thousands%20of%20homes%20in%20the%20region%20and%20created%20a%20mass%20build-up%20of%20debris%20that%20the%20city%20is%20now%20scrambling%20to%20collect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlorida%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_WwCbnhERdc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eduring%20a%20news%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20state%20has%20deployed%20over%20300%20dump%20trucks%20to%20collect%20debris%20in%20the%20hardest-hit%20areas.%20And%2C%20he%20added%2C%20the%20state's%20Department%20of%20Transportation%20alone%20has%20collected%20more%20than%201%2C200%20truckloads%20of%20debris%2C%20totaling%2022%2C000%20cubic%20yards%2C%20in%20just%20the%20past%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Friedman%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20College%20HUNKS%20Hauling%20Junk%20%26amp%3B%20Moving%20said%20after%20Helene%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20felt%20like%20a%20war%20zone%20in%20the%20subsequent%20days%20where%20literally%20everybody's%20belongings%20in%20their%20homes%20was%20out%20on%20the%20curb%20because%20their%20homes%20flooded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriedman's%20company%2C%20which%20has%20200%20franchise%20locations%20around%20the%20US%20but%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Tampa%2C%20was%20hired%20by%20the%20city%20of%20Tampa%20to%20help%20with%20the%20debris%20removal%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20had%20spent%20their%20lifetimes%20in%20Tampa%20said%20they've%20never%20experienced%20something%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20people%20were%20starting%20to%20get%20their%20bearings%20and%20spring%20into%20action%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20mess%2C%20Friedman%20said%2C%20then%20the%20second%20storm%20was%20forecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20people%20started%20really%20scrambling%20because%20I%20would%20say%20every%20other%20home%20you%20passed%20had%20a%20pile%20of%20at%20least%20a%20garage's%20worth%20of%20stuff%20out%20on%20their%20curb%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriedman's%20company%20has%20been%20operating%2050%20of%20its%20own%20junk%20and%20moving%20trucks%20since%20being%20hired%20by%20the%20city%2C%20collecting%20roughly%202%20million%20pounds%20of%20debris%20a%20day%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20debris%20gets%20dumped%20into%20landfills%20that%20are%20required%20to%20be%20open%2024%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20DeSantis%20said%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it's%20even%20more%20urgent%20to%20get%20the%20junk%20out%20of%20the%20way%20before%20Milton%20strikes%2C%20Marla%20Spence-Howell%2C%20the%20communications%20coordinator%20for%20Tampa's%20Solid%20Waste%20and%20Environmental%20Program%20Management%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20debris%20%E2%80%94%20fallen%20trees%2C%20drywall%2C%20appliances%2C%20broken%20furniture%2C%20cabinets%2C%20mattresses%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20left%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20when%20Milton%20hits%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20cause%20major%20hazards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20a%20hundred-plus%20mile%20winds%2C%20those%20things%20will%20turn%20into%20projectiles%20and%20get%20strewn%20all%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20Friedman%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20safe%20if%20that%20stuff%20hits%20your%20house%20or%20hits%20the%20window.%20It%20creates%20certainly%20a%20safety%20hazard.%20But%20it's%20definitely%20going%20to%20be%20a%20messy%2C%20messy%2C%20messy%20cleanup%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20hurricane-force%20winds%20that%20can%20make%20the%20debris%20more%20dangerous%20%E2%80%94%20flooding%20too%20can%20pick%20up%20objects%20and%20whip%20them%20around%2C%20Jeffrey%20Schlegelmilch%2C%20a%20research%20scholar%20and%20director%20for%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Disaster%20Preparedness%20at%20Columbia%20Climate%20School%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDebris%20removal%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20expenses%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20recovery%20because%20you%20just%20have%20massive%20amounts%20of%20damage%20and%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlegelmilch%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20you%20imagine%20another%20storm%20coming%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20creates%20a%20compounding%20effect%20that%20makes%20everything%20more%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20dangerous%2C%20Schlegelmilch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hardest%20hit%20regions%20of%20the%20state%2C%20debris%20removal%20will%20continue%20around%20the%20clock%20%26quot%3Buntil%20it's%20no%20longer%20safe%20to%20do%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20DeSantis%20said%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-milton-tampa-florida-desantis-clean-disaster-dangerous-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728436505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6705c04f198738e3a70f3ac3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-helene-milton-tampa-florida-desantis-clean-disaster-dangerous-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hurricane%20Milton%20is%20bearing%20down%20on%20Florida%2C%20and%20the%20region%20is%20still%20racing%20to%20clean%20up%20from%20Helene%2C%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40b