tion%2Ftutors%2Fcurrent-vacancies%2F%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20positions%3C%2Fa%3E%20paying%20between%20%24117%2C000%20and%20%24150%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20close%20relationship%20with%20the%20family%20is%20both%20a%20challenge%20and%20a%20reward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20relationship%20we%20develop%20with%20those%20families%20lasts%20many%20years%20after%20we%20finish%20tutoring%20their%20kid%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tutors%20International's%20Hannan.%20%26quot%3BMy%20professional%20obligations%20to%20a%20family%20expired%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20I'm%20happy%20to%20fly%20across%20an%20ocean%20and%20spend%20time%20with%20them%20on%20my%20dime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHannan%20said%20that%20candidates%20for%20Tutors%20International%20answer%20rigorous%20essay-style%20questions%20and%20undergo%20interviews%20before%20Caller%20shortlists%20two%20for%20a%20client.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20choice%20often%20comes%20down%20to%20which%20tutor%20the%20client%20connects%20with%20best%2C%20which%20Tutors%20International's%20Dunckley%20likened%20to%20matchmaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20while%20many%20tutors%20may%20have%20similar%20paper%20qualifications%2C%20their%20ability%20to%20meet%20the%20family's%20needs%20is%20usually%20the%20dealbreaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20family%20might%20want%20to%20travel%20and%20use%20the%20locations%20as%20inspiration%20for%20learning%2C%20and%20another%20needs%20their%20child%20to%20get%20into%20Harvard%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dunckley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20matching%20tutors%20with%20families%20goes%20beyond%20academic%20expertise.%20Dunckley%20says%20tutors%20and%20families%20must%20fit%20each%20other's%20personalities%20and%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20just%20showing%20up%2C%20teaching%20for%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20and%20then%20living%20your%20own%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20spending%20time%20with%20them%20in%20airports%20and%20dragging%20bags%20through%20high-stress%20situations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223818%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flight%20Cancellations%20Israel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe629e9e0c5c2eeeea40df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222617%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20constant%20traveling%20meant%20that%20high-stress%20situations%20from%20flight%20cancellations%20or%20delays%20were%20unavoidable%2C%20said%20Dunckley.%3Cp%3EChen%20Junqing%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0b5bab2-79fd-4a3c-936a-0fa4d2d5a3d2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfessionalism%20is%20a%20non-negotiable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20so%20closely%20with%20the%20families%20they%20tutor%20presents%20professional%20boundary%20challenges.%20Caller%20told%20BI%20of%20one%20tutor%20who%20learned%20this%20the%20hard%20way%20after%20being%20filmed%20drunk%20at%20a%20private%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20just%20go%20and%20have%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20with%20them%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Caller%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20your%20clients%20might%20be%20behaving%2C%20the%20tutor%20shouldn't%20have%20done%20that%2C%20but%20it's%20difficult%20for%20a%20tutor%20to%20get%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20tutors%20work%20and%20live%20close%20to%20their%20clients%2C%20maintaining%20boundaries%20becomes%20paramount.%20For%20Hannan%2C%20keeping%20a%20professional%20distance%20means%20adhering%20to%20one%20cardinal%20rule%3A%20Not%20living%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20hard%20to%20maintain%20a%20professional%20distance%20from%20your%20student%20if%20your%20bedroom%20is%20next%20to%20theirs%2C%26quot%3B%20Hannan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20there%20to%20do%20a%20job%2C%20and%20even%20though%20you%20might%20become%20friendly%20with%20the%20family%2C%20you're%20not%20their%20friend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeacon%20Education's%20Jones%20told%20BI%20of%20a%20tutor%20assigned%20to%20a%20Canadian%20family%20who%20spent%20a%20month%20in%20Thailand.%20While%20the%20family%20stayed%20at%20a%20homestay%2C%20the%20tutor%20organized%20accommodations%20in%20a%20separate%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20his%20company's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etutors%20typically%20do%20not%20live%20with%20the%20families%20they%20work%20for%2C%20as%20the%20arrangement%20can%20become%20overwhelming.%20Instead%2C%20tutors%20usually%20travel%20with%20the%20families%20and%20remain%20nearby%2C%20but%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20nannying%20their%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225014fe5a-0a88-419b-9852-42fd1d2df1ec%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDating%20takes%20a%20pause%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20constant%20travel%2C%20finding%20time%20for%20romance%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-private-jet-pilot-what-job-like-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20probably%20a%20big%20part%20of%20why%20I'm%20single%2C%26quot%3B%20Hannan%20said%20of%20his%20busy%20traveling%20schedule%20for%20the%20past%2018%20years.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20that%20I%20have%20to%20accept%20if%20this%20is%20something%20that%20I%20want%20to%20do%20for%20my%20career.%20So%20it's%20just%20par%20for%20the%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETutors%20International's%20Dunckley%20said%20that%20being%20a%20travel%20tutor%20is%20likely%20very%20difficult%20for%20tutors%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20close%20social%20network%26quot%3B%20and%20becomes%20much%20less%20suitable%20for%20tutors%20looking%20to%20settle%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dunckley%20had%20her%20child%2C%20residential%20assignments%20became%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%2C%20but%20much%20less%20flexible%2C%20once%20you%20have%20a%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dunckley%2C%20who%20completed%20a%20two-year%20role%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20traveling%20alongside%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunckley%20has%20since%20stopped%20travel%20tutoring%20and%2C%20after%20starting%20a%20family%2C%20took%20on%20a%20client%20account%20manager%20role%20at%20Tutors%20International%20from%20her%20home%20in%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de986c3c-bbe0-4fde-8272-b8d6d75ed24c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20all%20work%20and%20no%20play%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20usual%20school%20holidays%2C%20tutors%20are%20also%20given%20time%20off%20from%20their%20jobs%20to%20unwind%20and%20explore%20the%20cities%20they're%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunckley%20said%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etutors%20must%20weave%20their%20off-time%20into%20wherever%20they%20are%2C%20even%20out%20at%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20in%20Tonga%2C%20I%20took%20a%20day%20off%20and%20dropped%20off%20the%20side%20of%20the%20boat%20in%20the%20kayak%20and%20disappeared%20into%20the%20day%2C%20the%20island%2C%20and%20just%20sort%20of%20chilled%20with%20a%20boat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dunckley.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20where%20you%20can%20plan%20to%20be%20off%20on%20weekends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDunckley%20also%20said%20tutors%20have%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Elearn%20to%20balance%20their%20time%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-hobbies-connect-find-creativity-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20find%20hobbies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthat%20you%20can%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20you're%20not%20hyper-alert%20the%20whole%20time.%26quot%3B%20Dunckley%20said%20that%20she%20relaxed%20by%20reading%20a%20book%20or%20visiting%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20good%20if%20you%20burn%20out%20and%20are%20resentful%20or%20unhappy%2C%26quot%3B%20Dunckley%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20just%20making%20sure%20that%20when%20I%20did%20have%20the%20time%2C%20I%20made%20the%20most%20of%20it%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20just%20sit%20and%20stew%20or%20worry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224602%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tonga%20Sailboat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fe60ef7de5c8fd4834e4cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222953%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20day%20off%20for%20Dunckley%20sometimes%20meant%20making%20the%20most%20out%20of%20alone%20time%20on%20a%20boat.%3Cp%3EBodo%20M%C3%BCller%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20constant%20traveling%20satisfied%20Dunckley's%20wanderlust%2C%20she%20said%20that%20the%20most%20fulfilling%20part%20of%20her%20job%20was%20being%20a%20part%20of%20her%20students'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20the%20educational%20stuff.%20It's%20the%20life%20stuff%20too%2C%20like%20changing%20the%20tire%20on%20a%20car%2C%20figuring%20out%20where%20you're%20going%2C%20and%20getting%20laundry%20done%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20nowhere%20in%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20Dunckley%20said.%20%26quot%3BChildren%20benefit%20from%20having%20somebody%20on%20their%20side%2C%20building%20their%20confidence%20as%20role%20models%20and%20mentors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20around%20or%20for%20high-net-worth%20individuals%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Alwee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Elwee%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-tutors-salaries-teaching-downsides-dating-wealthy-vacation-students-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728432002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ec8ea8d17aa3c7b2b45e16%3Fformat%3D