money-6-figures-month%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobux%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20In%20theory%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20way%20for%20them%20to%20be%20creative%20and%20learn%20a%20little%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20user-generated%20content%20also%20means%20some%20games%20are%20not%20exactly%20high-quality%20%E2%80%94%20or%20they%20appeal%20to%20kids'%20worst%20impulses%20(toilet%20humor%2C%20cartoon%20violence%2C%20unapproved%20use%20of%20intellectual%20property).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20browsing%20around%20Tuesday%2C%20I%20saw%20horror%20games%20and%20gun-themed%20games%20rated%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20ages.%26quot%3B%20Many%20games%20appear%20to%20play%20fast-and-loose%20with%20intellectual%20property%3A%20Peppa%20Pig%2C%20SpongeBob%2C%20and%20Mickey%20Mouse%20all%20make%20very%20likely%20unauthorized%20appearances%20in%20various%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20games%20that%20weren't%20necessarily%20violent%20or%20sexual%20but%20had%20weird%20body%20stuff%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BFat%20Race%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BGet%20Fat%20and%20Roll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roblox%20games%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6705b6dca703186492806832%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20Roblox%20games%20rated%20%26quot%3Ball%20ages.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERoblox%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Hindenburg%20Research%2C%20a%20short-seller%2C%20published%20a%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Froblox-stock-price-short-seller-hindenburg-report-gaming-inflated-metrics-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccusing%20Roblox%20of%20inflating%20user%20metrics%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20deceiving%20investors.%20The%20company's%20stock%20fell%20more%20than%209%25%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20report%20but%20recouped%20some%20of%20its%20losses%20and%20ended%20up%20down%202.13%25%20on%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Roblox%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20totally%20reject%20the%20claims%20made%20in%20the%20report.%20The%20financial%20claims%20made%20by%20Hindenburg%20Research%20are%20simply%20misleading.%20The%20authors%20are%2C%20admittedly%20short-sellers%20and%20have%20an%20agenda%20irrespective%20of%20the%20substance%20of%20Roblox'%20business%20model%20and%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindenburg%20report%20also%20accused%20Roblox%20of%20%26quot%3Bexposing%20children%20to%20grooming%2C%20pornography%2C%20violent%20content%2C%20and%20extremely%20abusive%20speech.%26quot%3B%20Roblox%20disagreed%2C%20saying%20it's%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20and%20secure%20platform.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHindenburg's%20report%20wasn't%20the%20first%20to%20detail%20concerns%20about%20children%20using%20the%20platform.%20In%20July%2C%20Bloomberg%20published%20a%20story%20that%20it%20titled%20%26quot%3BRoblox's%20Pedophile%20Problem.%26quot%3B%20(Roblox's%20chief%20safety%20officer%20told%20Bloomberg%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20platform%20didn't%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20child%20safety.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20exploration%20of%20the%20platform%2C%20I%20found%20that%20parents%20can%20disable%20the%20%26quot%3Bchat%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20which%20can%20ease%20some%20worries%20about%20children%20talking%20to%20adults.%20But%20this%20doesn't%20address%20my%20issues%20with%20the%20games'%20actual%20content%2C%20some%20of%20which%20dealt%20with%20sexual%20and%20violent%20themes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhindenburgresearch.com%2Froblox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindenburg's%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20my%20attention%20as%20a%20parent.%20I%20didn't%20access%20these%20games%20myself%2C%20but%20the%20bullets%20below%20are%20from%20Hindenburg%2C%20in%20the%20short-seller's%20own%20words%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUsers%20seeking%20sexual%20experiences%20on%20Roblox%20are%20so%20pervasive%20that%20there%20are%20thousands%20of%20Roblox%20sex%20videos%20on%20porn%20sites%2C%20inviting%20users%20of%20unknown%20ages%20to%20make%20explicit%20content%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20tested%20out%20Roblox's%20experiences%20to%20see%20what%20else%20kids%20were%20being%20exposed%20to.%20We%20quickly%20encountered%20images%20of%20male%20genitalia%20and%20hate%20speech%20in%20Roblox's%20%26quot%3Bschool%20simulator%26quot%3B%20game%2C%20which%20had%20registered%2028.9%20million%20visits%20with%20no%20age%20restrictions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20the%20company's%20mission%20%26quot%3Bto%20connect%20a%20billion%20users%20with%20optimism%20and%20civility%26quot%3B%2C%20we%20found%20games%20such%20as%20%26quot%3BBeat%20Up%20Homeless%20Outside%207%2F11%20Simulator%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20had%201%20million%20visits%20and%2015%2C000%20favorites%20before%20being%20removed%20from%20Roblox.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENonetheless%2C%20Roblox%20users%20identifying%20as%209%20years%20old%20and%20up%20can%20still%20beat%20up%20homeless%20people%20in%20%26quot%3BBeat%20Up%20People%20Outside%20of%207%2F11%26quot%3B%20with%20over%20900%2C000%20visits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20game%20%26quot%3BBeat%20Up%20The%20Pregnant%26quot%3B%2C%20users%20hacked%20pregnant%20women%20to%20death%20in%20a%20Wal-Mart%20parking%20lot%20with%20machetes%20or%20killed%20them%20with%20frying%20pans%20or%20a%20selection%20of%20guns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20played%20%26quot%3B%5BGUNS%5D%20Work%20at%20a%20Hospital%26quot%3B%20where%20users%20can%20go%20on%20a%20hospital%20shooting%20rampage.%20The%20game%20has%20~1.6%20million%20visits%20and%20remains%20on%20the%20platform%20with%20no%20age%20restrictions.%20The%20game's%20thumbnail%20is%20a%20picture%20of%20a%20terrified%20pregnant%20woman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Roblox%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%