icular%20challenges%20due%20to%20inadequate%20waste%20management%20practices.%20Although%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20reduce%20plastic%20consumption%2C%20this%20alone%20is%20insufficient%20to%20tackle%20the%20escalating%20problem%20of%20plastic%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadquartered%20in%20London%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20partnered%20with%20the%20startup%20%E2%80%98Plastics%20for%20Change%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20launch%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebodyshop.in%2Fabout-us%2Factivism%2Fcommunity-trade-recycled-plastic%2Fe%2Fe00010%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECommunity%20Fair%20Trade%20Recycled%20Plastic%3C%2Fa%3E%20programme%20in%202019%2C%20aiming%20to%20incorporate%20community-traded%20recycled%20plastic%20into%20its%20best-selling%20products%20while%20helping%20to%20empower%20waste%20pickers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20buys%20recycled%20plastic%20collected%20by%20waste%20collectors%20in%20a%20number%20of%20centres%20including%20Bengaluru%2C%20incorporating%20it%20into%20the%20packaging%20after%20thorough%20cleaning%20and%20converting%20it%20to%20recycled%20granules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%20image%20(L%20to%20R)%3A%20Lakshmavva%2C%20Gangavva%2C%20Saraswati%2C%20and%20Jayanthi%3B%20Right%20image%3A%20Shakunthala%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdCqw0lKR5M9ne9VF9mvnHSo886Zchoo3NPKdWblcC17TyIcuAd_xapehtBNMuX6dZDoFnq4qDD2Tb5LCzmhHCvcwht_rmB6VnOO6fcCFeW8rcXg-Iy3-ptJ6-xcD3AWP8nXtdhnsOUC0IHReYqEWHHK8nWLOybcR2skcP8ytteGaID4fA2oA%3Fkey%3DN9hf2spKjjJNMZc-gLRwCg%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELeft%20image%20(L%20to%20R)%3A%20Lakshmavva%2C%20Gangavva%2C%20Saraswati%2C%20and%20Jayanthi%3B%20Right%20image%3A%20Shakunthala%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Body%20Shop%20started%20by%20integrating%20Plastics%20For%20Change%20material%20into%20one%20product%20line%20(shampoos)%20and%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%2014%20product%20lines%2C%20including%20all%20PET%20bottles%20and%20jars.%20This%20expansion%20covers%20body%20and%20hair%20care%20products%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20skincare%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShriti%20Malhotra%2C%20Group%20CEO%20of%20Quest%20Retail%20The%20Body%20Shop%20India%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Body%20Shop%20and%20Plastics%20for%20Change%20collaborated%20with%20an%20ambitious%20goal%20of%20not%20just%20using%20recycled%20plastic%20but%20using%20plastic%20as%20a%20resource%20to%20uplift%20the%20lives%20of%20thousands%20of%20informal%20waste%20workers.%20Socially%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20created%20meaningful%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20marginalised%20communities.%20Importantly%2C%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20those%20involved%20in%20our%20partnership%20are%20women%2C%20contributing%20to%20gender%20equality%20in%20the%20workforce.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlastics%20for%20Change%20has%20been%20actively%20working%20to%20uplift%20the%20lives%20of%20waste%20collectors%20and%20their%20families.%20The%20programme%20also%20provides%20access%20to%20essential%20social%20services%20such%20as%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20and%20financial%20support%2C%20fostering%20holistic%20well-being%20within%20these%20communities.%20It%20empowers%20women%20waste%20collectors%20to%20become%20entrepreneurs%20and%20achieve%20financial%20independence%2C%20helping%20to%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20and%20promoting%20gender%20equality%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20fighting%20plastic%20pollution%20to%20championing%20waste%20collector%20rights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20addressing%20plastic%20pollution%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20is%20collaborating%20with%20waste%20collectors%20%E2%80%94%20who%20are%20often%20the%20unsung%20heroes%20of%20waste%20management%20%E2%80%94%20to%20reshape%20the%20narrative%20surrounding%20waste%20management%20and%20improve%20their%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20approximately%201.5%20million%20waste%20pickers%2C%20with%20around%20half%20a%20million%20being%20women%2C%20work%20tirelessly%20each%20day%20to%20clean%20the%20streets%20and%20cities.%20Unfortunately%2C%20many%20of%20these%20individuals%20face%20discrimination%20and%20endure%20poor%20working%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20N.A.R.I%20(Nutrition.%20Ability.%20Retraining.%20Inclusion)%20was%20launched%20to%20address%20key%20challenges%20faced%20by%20waste%20collectors%2C%20especially%20women%2C%20who%20work%20in%20hazardous%20conditions%2C%20facing%20increased%20exposure%20to%20contaminated%20waste%20without%20adequate%20protective%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20initiative%2C%20100%20women%20waste%20collectors%20were%20provided%20PPE%20(personal%20protective%20equipment)%20kits%2C%20essential%20to%20reducing%20their%20health%20risks.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20received%20daily%20meals%2C%20protein%2C%20and%20vitamin%20supplements%2C%20aimed%20at%20combating%20malnutrition%20and%20improving%20their%20overall%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20also%20promoted%20financial%20inclusion%20by%20facilitating%20access%20to%20banking%20systems%20and%20government%20schemes.%20For%20every%20kilogram%20of%20plastic%20traded%2C%20women%20received%20cash%20incentives%20directly%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%20fostering%20savings%20habits%20and%20ensuring%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjula%2C%20a%20dedicated%20waste%20collector%2C%20has%20been%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20beneficiary%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20Through%20their%20partnership%2C%20she%20gained%20access%20to%20an%20electric%20tricycle%2C%20which%20has%20significantly%20improved%20her%20ability%20to%20collect%20more%20waste%20each%20day.%20This%20ultimately%20increased%20her%20income.%20With%20a%20stable%20income%2C%20Manjula%20has%20been%20able%20to%20ensure%20her%20daughter%20has%20the%20education%20that%20she%20herself%20never%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20cost%20and%20impact%20in%20recycling%20initiatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transformative%20impact%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebodyshop.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Body%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99s%20collaboration%20with%20Plastics%20for%20Change%20is%20evident%20through%20stories%20like%20that%20of%20Manjula%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjula%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXd0q9fjjroutCc1rRCxzBT121aWc0AvgqG3lUiS4ul738yO9Vgzuwal2JO_U3U4tutzNqJa0Yw9O0bTAHSOLO-K9rTD7_D4JLlEIjI5nKjvjVy0s5kD88f7gS4v4jmKQpBzATymALUhXoq4WrAlsU2Jg9vg5k-5ZyedKwDFwikGIyfC1zwhqJk%3Fkey%3DN9hf2spKjjJNMZc-gLRwCg%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EManjula%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20challenges%20faced%20while%20scaling%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20various%20initiatives%2C%20Andrew%20Almack%2C%20founder%20and%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20(CEO)%20of%20Plastics%20for%20Change%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20Plastics%20For%20Change%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20power%20of%20responsible%20sourcing%20practices%20to%20transform%20lives.%20Our%20collaboration%20with%20The%20Body%20Shop%20goes%20beyond%20addressing%20plastic%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20creating%20lasting%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20informal%20waste%20collectors.%20Through%20fair%20trade%20practices%20and%20community-driven%20impact%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20ensuring%20that%20the%20very%20plastic%20that%20threatens%20our%20environment%20can%20become%20a%20tool%20