0at%20least%2030%20local%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CDepending%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20tree%2C%20we%20pay%20Rs%205%20and%20Rs%2025%20per%20tree.%20Now%2C%20they%20are%20not%20just%20earning%20by%20selling%20fruit%20but%20also%20tree%20waste.%20Sometimes%2C%20many%20farmers%20do%20not%20accept%20money%2C%20as%20this%20process%20benefits%20them%20in%20clearing%20fields.%20This%20saves%20them%20labour%20costs%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jagat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeaving%20no%20waste%20behind%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20extracting%20fibre%20from%20banana%20tree%20waste%2C%20the%20startup%20makes%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products%20from%20banana%20fibre%20folders%2C%20yoga%20mats%2C%20baskets%2C%20paintings%2C%20cushion%20covers%2C%20coasters%2C%20and%20more.%20While%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20maintains%20a%20zero-waste%20approach%20in%20all%20its%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20utilises%20the%20leftover%20pulp%20from%20the%20fibre%20extraction%20and%20processes%20it%20into%20high-quality%20vermicompost.%20Furthermore%2C%20Taruwar%20extracts%20banana%20liquid%20from%20the%20pulp%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20a%20natural%20fertiliser%20rich%20in%20micronutrients%20like%20potassium%20and%20iron.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20everything%20in%20the%20process%20is%20turned%20into%20something%20valuable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20and%20social%20impact%20has%20garnered%20significant%20traction%2C%20with%20an%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20in%20the%20previous%20financial%20year.%20Every%20month%2C%20the%20startup%20utilises%20up%20to%20600%20kg%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264157%2Fbanana-fibre-earns-lakhs-waste-business-success-ecofriendly-handicraft%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanana%20fibres%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20waste.%20Through%20off