0woman%20supports%20an%20abuse%20survivor.%20What%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20our%20duty%3B%20we%20need%20to%20celebrate%20the%20survivors%20instead.%20Just%20like%20moral%20values%20are%20taught%20in%20school%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20teach%20gender%20equality%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gorky%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gorky%20his%20wife%2C%20with%20her%20courage%20and%20ability%20to%20stand%20strong%20and%20fight%2C%20remains%20a%20true%20inspiration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20very%20courageous%2C%20happy%20going%20girl.%20She%20accepts%20life%20as%20it%20comes%2C%20lives%20in%20the%20present%2C%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Her%20life%20has%20been%20a%20struggle%2C%20and%20the%20way%20she%20handled%20problems%20by%20herself%20at%20a%20young%20age%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20her.%C2%A0%20Even%20when%20she%20had%20to%20go%20to%20court%20for%20her%20divorce%2C%20she%20was%20confident%20and%20carried%20herself%20exceptionally%20well.%20She%20is%20a%20true%20inspiration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Priyatama%20is%20at%20peace%20with%20herself%20and%20is%20slowly%20taking%20steps%20to%20heal%20her%20trauma%20with%20the%20help%20of%20therapy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20would%20shiver%20and%20feel%20cold%20just%20thinking%20about%20those%20incidents.%20I%E2%80%99m%20working%20my%20way%20out%20of%20that.%20My%20body%20is%20just%20a%20body%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20my%20identity.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ever%20let%20anyone%20make%20you%20feel%20less%20than%20you%20are%20because%20of%20the%20abuse%20inflicted%20on%20you.%20We%20are%20more%20than%20our%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priyatama%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20creating%20a%20better%20India%20for%2